df>。\\\\[引用于第[1.](#_bookmark0)\\\\]\\n22. Chelsea Komlo和Ian Goldberg。Frost:灵活的回合优化Schnorr阈值签名。Cryp- tology ePrint Archive, Report 2020/852, 2020. <https://eprint.iacr.org/2020/852>. \\\\[引用于第 [6.](#_bookmark5)\\\\]\\n23. Jae Kwon和Ethan Buchman。宇宙。一个分布式账本的网络。\\n\\n    <https://cosmos.network/resources/whitepaper>。\\\\[引自第和[1](#_bookmark0)页[2.](#_bookmark1)\\\\]\\n24. 雪崩团队。雪崩平台。\\n\\n    <https://www.avalabs.org/whitepapers>。 \\\\[引自第和[1](#_bookmark0)页[2](#_bookmark1).\\\\]\\n25. 加文-伍德Polkadot:一个异质多链框架的愿景。\\n\\n    <https://polkadot.network/PolkaDotPaper.pdf>。\\\\[引自第和[1](#_bookmark0)页[2.](#_bookmark1)\\\\]\",\"timestamp\":1642002774,\"title\":\"Axelar白皮书中文版\"},\"digest\":\"3mlIVgtyKDnQIgdrhypvLlxuGXruwnj7919I_dFtGVg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x9b8CAcbB725E933584b9D732df934801Db2391be\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"hzDKfhxWsb-ZTyz1hBC6eapQ55tWPbdZLtcWC9WDHlU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"vb2SlGKuxvauSX1j5sUApIZN_p1fjQQNlU4yYmYykiw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"iAK_4JDaRO1oMjWqSViQbObLtRzsRWRxtYx1d9fVtAAx7gD-uVIbdO-tTfQogaYCna77ryKskDnyHgYSU4biig\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x5e26df33c2452aa2684779c1151a2f25bf60055570c5f851757cd85ba40d06f870861d8f64ce0ce2a7c25af2a617ae9a765942e3b13ce317572e5d2db1a3f5e11b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"hzDKfhxWsb-ZTyz1hBC6eapQ55tWPbdZLtcWC9WDHlU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"vb2SlGKuxvauSX1j5sUApIZN_p1fjQQNlU4yYmYykiw\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"3mlIVgtyKDnQIgdrhypvLlxuGXruwnj7919I_dFtGVg\"}"